        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1160",
        "content": "He then show'd me his piece for my opinion, and I much approv'd it, as it appear'd to me to have great merit.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
